Enum DocumentAtom.SlideSize

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DocumentAtom.SlideSize>
      • org.apache.poi.hslf.record.DocumentAtom.SlideSize
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<DocumentAtom.SlideSize>
    Enclosing class:
    DocumentAtom 

    public static enum DocumentAtom.SlideSize
extends java.lang.Enum<DocumentAtom.SlideSize>
    Holds the different Slide Size values(保存不同的幻灯片大小值)

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      A4_SIZED_PAPER
      Slide size ratio is consistent with A4 paper.(载玻片大小比例与A4纸一致。)
      BANNER
      Slide size ratio is consistent with a banner.(幻灯片大小比例与横幅一致。)
      CUSTOM
      Slide size ratio that is not consistent with any of the other specified slide sizes in this enumeration.(幻灯片大小比率与此列举中任何其他指定的幻灯片大小不一致。)
      LETTER_SIZED_PAPER
      Slide size ratio is consistent with letter paper.(幻灯片尺寸比例与信纸一致。)
      ON_35MM
      Slide size ratio is consistent with 35mm photo slides.(载玻片尺寸比例与35 mm照片载玻片一致。)
      ON_SCREEN
      Slide size ratio is consistent with a computer screen.(幻灯片大小比例与电脑屏幕一致。)
      OVERHEAD
      Slide size ratio is consistent with overhead projector slides.(幻灯片大小比例与高架投影仪幻灯片一致。)
